OL,3,CGTA developer accused of sacking 30
OL,4,Cstaff in 'union-busting' move
OL,6,FA union has claimed that more than 30
OL,7,FUK staff at Rockstar Games, the
OL,8,Fdeveloper behind Grand Theft Auto,
OL,9,Fhave been sacked in what it described
OL,10,Fas a "union-busting" move by
OL,11,Fmanagement.
OL,13,FThe Independent Workers' Union of
OL,14,FGreat Britain (IWGB) has claimed that
OL,15,Fstaff at Rockstar Games' Edinburgh
OL,16,Fbase were sacked for "trade union
OL,17,Factivity," describing the dismissals
OL,18,Fas "unlawful and retaliatory".
