OL,6,FThe union said all of the affected
OL,7,Femployees were members of both the
OL,8,FIWGB and a private chat group on the
OL,9,FDiscord app.
OL,11,FRockstar Games, the developer behind
OL,12,Fthe Grand Theft Auto franchise and a
OL,13,Fsubsidiary of Take-Two Interactive,
OL,14,Fhas made more than $8 billion (#6
OL,15,Fbillion) from GTA 5 since its release
OL,16,Fin 2013, making it the most profitable
OL,17,Fvideo game in history.
OL,19,FTake-Two said the employees were
OL,20,Fdismissed for "gross misconduct".
