OL,4,Cstaff in 'union-busting' move
OL,6,FThe IWGB said in a statement: "Over 30
OL,7,Fmembers of UK staff at Rockstar Games,
OL,8,Fdevelopers of the Grand Theft Auto
OL,9,Fseries, were fired on Thursday October
OL,10,F30 due to trade union activity.
OL,12,F"The staff, who were all part of a
OL,13,Fprivate trade union Discord channel
OL,14,Fand members of the Independent
OL,15,FWorkers' Union of Great Britain, were
OL,16,Fdismissed in what the union argues
OL,17,Fconstitutes unlawful and retaliatory
OL,18,Fdismissals.
OL,26,@nD@_OUtD@AOU
