OL,3,CGTA developer accused of sacking 30
OL,4,Cstaff in 'union-busting' move
OL,6,F"Organisers at the IWGB have reported
OL,7,Fthat amongst the staff dismissed were
OL,8,Fthose with visas sponsored by Rockstar
OL,9,Fand those with medical conditions who
OL,10,Fwill lose access to essential
OL,11,Fworkplace healthcare schemes.
OL,13,F"The IWGB, which sees this as a brazen
OL,14,Fact of illegal union busting, says it
OL,15,Fwill be mounting a full and robust
OL,16,Fdefence of its members who it believes
OL,17,Fhave been targeted unfairly for
OL,18,Fexercising their legal rights."
