OL,4,Cstaff in 'union-busting' move
OL,6,FAlex Marshall, IWGB president, said:
OL,7,F"Rockstar has just carried out the
OL,8,Fmost blatant and ruthless act of union
OL,9,Fbusting in the history of the games
OL,10,Findustry.
OL,12,F"This flagrant contempt for the law
OL,13,Fand for the lives of the workers who
OL,14,Fbring in their billions is an insult
OL,15,Fto their fans and the global industry.
OL,17,F"Despite this calculated attack on
OL,18,Fworkers organising for a collective
OL,19,Fvoice and to improve their difficult
OL,20,Fworking conditions, the Rockstar union
OL,21,Fremains undeterred.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
