OL,6,F"They will keep organising for respect
OL,7,Fand better conditions whilst
OL,8,Fcontinuing to pour their blood, sweat
OL,9,Fand creativity into games that are
OL,10,Floved by millions.
OL,12,F"The IWGB will pursue every legal
OL,13,Fclaim possible to ensure our members
OL,14,Fare reinstated and receive interim
OL,15,Frelief."
