OL,6,FSpring McParlin-Jones, chair of the
OL,7,FIWGB Game Workers Union, said: "Next
OL,8,Fyear, Grand Theft Auto VI is expected
OL,9,Fto make upwards of 10 billion dollars
OL,10,F(#7.6 billion).
OL,12,F"That's enough to end world hunger for
OL,13,Fa year. Such a flagrant attack on
OL,14,Fworkers' rights from such a valuable
OL,15,Fstudio sends a very clear and shocking
OL,16,Fmessage to the world, that money
OL,17,Fmatters more than people."
