OL,6,FAlan Lewis, head of global corporate
OL,7,Fcommunications at Take Two
OL,8,FInteractive, said: "We strive to make
OL,9,Fthe world's best entertainment
OL,10,Fproperties by giving our best-in-class
OL,11,Fcreative teams positive work
OL,12,Fenvironments and ongoing career
OL,13,Fopportunities.
OL,15,F"Our culture is focused on teamwork,
OL,16,Fexcellence, and kindness. Rockstar
OL,17,FGames terminated a small number of
OL,18,Findividuals for gross misconduct, and
OL,19,Ffor no other reason. As always, we
OL,20,Ffully support Rockstar's ambitions and
OL,21,Fapproach."
